  <brief_title>Spironolactone With Patiromer in the Treatment of Resistant Hypertension in Chronic Kidney Disease</brief_title>
  <acronym>AMBER</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo Controlled, Parallel Group Study of Patiromer for the Enablement of Spironolactone Use for Blood Pressure Control in Patients With Resistant Hypertension and Chronic Kidney Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
